# Technology Stack — Shortly

## Stack Overview

| Layer | Technology | Version | Role |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Runtime** | React | ^18.3.1 | UI library |
| **Build Tool** | Vite | ^6.4.2 | Dev server & bundler (SWC transpiler) |
| **Routing** | React Router | ^7.14.0 | Client-side routing |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS | 4.2.2 | Utility-first CSS (v4 CSS-first architecture) |
| **Component Library** | DaisyUI | 5.5.19 | Semantic Tailwind component classes |
| **Icons** | @iconify/react | 5.0.1 | Universal icon library (on-demand SVG) |
| **Class Merging** | clsx + tailwind-merge | 2.1.1 / 2.4.0 | `cn()` utility for conditional + conflict-free classes |
| **Linting** | ESLint | ^9.39.4 | Code quality (Flat Config format) |
| **Formatting** | Prettier | 3.3.2 | Code formatting + Tailwind class sorting |
| **Deployment** | gh-pages | 6.1.1 | GitHub Pages deployment |
| **Package Manager** | pnpm | — | Fast, disk-efficient package manager |

